org.intellimate.izou.sdk.resource

Class Resource<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intellimate.izou.sdk.resource.Resource<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable, ResourceModel<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BroadcasterAvailablePlaylists, BroadcasterPlaylist, CapabilitiesResource, CommandResource, MusicErrorResource, NowPlayingResource, PlaybackStateResource, PlayerResource, PlaylistResource, PresenceResource, ProgressResource, SelectorResource, TrackInfoResource, UsingSoundResource, VolumeResource

    public class Resource<T>
extends Object
implements ResourceModel<T>
    An Resource is an object which is used to pass data from one part of the application to another. Note! This Object is immutable!
